{
  "texts": [
    "Considering the importance of measurements in echo studies, we attempted to evaluate whether the current automatic metrics can detect changes in measurement numbers.",
    "For this purpose, we generated synthetic reports by replacing all the measurement numbers with random numbers ranging from 1 to 99 in the reports.",
    "We then compared the automatic metric scores with the corresponding reports with the original measurements.",
    "Human expert evaluation metrics: We designed a human expert evaluation process based on previous clinical text summarization studies 13, 18, 26.",
    "The Findings with corresponding ground truth (Final Impression) and LLM-generated summarization of 30 randomly selected cases were presented to four echocardiography-board-certified cardiologists for blinded quality review."
  ]
}